{"type":"message","id":"9a19bd55","parentId":"c9cf6a4c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:38:25.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the SKILL.md file for web search.","thinkingSignature":"cef2b87e18b1cb3fb1969f0e5c5ece8346d77f4bb4af56f719acec274f10bee6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ps2ngr62rquo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8972,"output":56,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53009,"cost":{"input":0.0026915999999999997,"output":0.0000672,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0040782299999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774672703637}}
{"type":"message","id":"68faa73c","parentId":"9a19bd55","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:38:25.624Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ps2ngr62rquo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774672705620}}
{"type":"message","id":"ccb895f2","parentId":"68faa73c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T04:38:29.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand how to use the web search. Let me search for information about enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services - specifically relevant to 道简网络's industry.","thinkingSignature":"562eb684d86b19fe3ac82ff1cc61211c36f066f4e75c03c02e7048be00373969"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d0k6qk3o8suf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策 趋势\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"CLI not available\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9543,"output":108,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53632,"cost":{"input":0.0028629,"output":0.0001296,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00431193}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774672705623}}
